PN,30201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780481194
OL,3,CAnimals that could replace figures
OL,4,Clike Winston Churchill on banknotes
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FA buff-tailed bumblebee, a dolphin, a
OL,8,Ffox, a butterfly, an owl and a shark
OL,9,Fare among the animals that could
OL,10,Freplace historical figures such as Sir
OL,11,FWinston Churchill on banknotes.
OL,13,FWorking with a panel of wildlife
OL,14,Fexperts, the Bank of England has
OL,15,Fproduced a shortlist set to become the
OL,16,Fcentral image on #5, #10, #20 and #50
OL,17,Fnotes.
OL,19,FBut the plan to remove the likes of
OL,20,FSir Winston faced a backlash from
OL,21,Fpoliticians earlier this year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780481194
OL,3,CAnimals that could replace figures
OL,4,Clike Winston Churchill on banknotes
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,8,Faccused the government of "erasing our
OL,9,Fhistory".
OL,11,FLib Dem Leader Sir Ed Davey said
OL,12,FChurchill, who helped defeat fascism
OL,13,Fin Europe, "deserves better than being
OL,14,Freplaced by a badger", while Reform
OL,15,FUK's leader Nigel Farage called the
OL,16,Fproposals "PC mad and loony".
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@HO]uD@LOUvD@UO]xD@KOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780481194
OL,3,CAnimals that could replace figures
OL,4,Clike Winston Churchill on banknotes
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FThe public is urged to have their say
OL,8,Fon which animals and birds will appear
OL,9,Fon the next series, spelling an end
OL,10,Ffor sometimes controversial characters
OL,11,Fwhich have featured for more than 50
OL,12,Fyears.
OL,14,FAnimals like mackerel, otters and red
OL,15,Fsquirrels already feature on the Royal
OL,16,FBank of Scotland's polymer banknotes
OL,17,Fas part of their "Fabric of Nature"
OL,18,Fseries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780481194
OL,3,CAnimals that could replace figures
OL,4,Clike Winston Churchill on banknotes
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FIn a consultation launched on
OL,8,FWednesday, the list has been grouped
OL,9,Finto three categories, covering a
OL,10,Fvariety of species and environments.
OL,12,FEach banknote will feature a different
OL,13,Fanimal designed to be difficult to
OL,14,Fcounterfeit.
OL,16,FPeople are being asked to select up to
OL,17,Ftwo examples from each category in the
OL,18,Fconsultation, which runs until 11.59pm
OL,19,Fon July 3.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780481194
OL,3,CAnimals that could replace figures
OL,4,Clike Winston Churchill on banknotes
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FThe central bank said that only the
OL,8,Fanimals on the shortlist can feature
OL,9,Fas the central images on the new
OL,10,Fseries, and it is not seeking
OL,11,Falternative nominations.
OL,13,FBank of England Governor Andrew Bailey
OL,14,Fwill make the final decision, taking
OL,15,Finto account feedback from the public,
OL,16,Fin particular UK residents and British
OL,17,Fcitizens living abroad. They can be
OL,18,Fsubmitted via the Bank's website or by
OL,19,Fpost.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780481194
OL,3,CAnimals that could replace figures
OL,4,Clike Winston Churchill on banknotes
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FThe Bank will announce the outcome of
OL,8,Fits consultation by the end of 2026.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FIt is likely to take a few years
OL,16,Fbefore the new notes enter circulation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780481194
OL,3,CAnimals that could replace figures
OL,4,Clike Winston Churchill on banknotes
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FVictoria Cleland, Bank of England
OL,8,Fchief cashier, said: "I very much hope
OL,9,Fthe public will enjoy engaging in our
OL,10,Fconsultation to choose the animals to
OL,11,Ffeature on our next series of
OL,12,Fbanknotes.
OL,14,F"The shortlisted animals demonstrate
OL,15,Fthe rich variety of wildlife we have
OL,16,Fto celebrate in the UK."
OL,26,@pD@VOUvD@AOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780481194
OL,3,CAnimals that could replace figures
OL,4,Clike Winston Churchill on banknotes
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FPeople will continue to see a human
OL,8,Fface as they take banknotes out of
OL,9,Ftheir wallets, even when animals are
OL,10,Fintroduced into designs, as the next
OL,11,Fseries will continue to include a
OL,12,Fportrait of the monarch.
OL,14,FRepresentation of the home nations
OL,15,Fwill also be an important feature in
OL,16,Fthe design, the Bank said.
OL,18,FHistorical figures who have helped
OL,19,Fshape thought, innovation, leadership
OL,20,Fand values have been showcased on
OL,21,Fbanknotes since 1970.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780481194
OL,3,CAnimals that could replace figures
OL,4,Clike Winston Churchill on banknotes
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FThe first of the current series has
OL,8,Fbeen in circulation since 2016, when
OL,9,F#5 banknotes featuring Sir Winston
OL,10,Fwere issued.
OL,12,FJane Austen is showcased on the #10,
OL,13,FJMW Turner on the #20 and Alan Turing
OL,14,Fon the #50.
OL,16,FThe rise in payments technology such
OL,17,Fas contactless and mobile wallets has
OL,18,Fgiven people an increasing array of
OL,19,Falternatives to banknotes and coins.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
