PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780481194
OL,3,CAnimals that could replace figures
OL,4,Clike Winston Churchill on banknotes
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FCash remains the preferred payment
OL,8,Fmethod for about one in seven people
OL,9,Fand the amount in circulation reached
OL,10,F#91.5 billion at the end of February
OL,11,F2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
